Dependencies
============
Python 2.7+
scipy
pylab
pykalman
pandas

Contents
========

Scripts
-------

sampler.py
    Main script to create and execute Gibbs sampler

simulate_data.py
    Script to generate data from model

vis_results.py
    Script to produce visualization of sampler results.

vis_data.py
    Script to produce visualization of data/simulation.

ffbs_test.py
    Script to test FFBS implementation correctness.

Modules
-------

gibbs.py
	Library containing Model and Gibbs sampler classes

misc.py
    Miscellaneous and FFBS algorithm

stats_util.py
    Miscellaneous random variable classes/functions

model_simulation_alpha.py
    Model spec and FCPs for simulation alpha: g and sigma_g sampling

model_simulation_beta.py
    Model spec and FCPs for simulation beta: g and sigma_g sampling with noise

model_simulation_gamma.py
    Model spec and FCPs for simulation beta: g, h, sigma_g, sigma_h, proportions, and types

model_simulation_gamma.py
    Model spec and FCPs for simulation beta: g, h, sigma_g, sigma_h, proportions, and types with noise


